dc_title_s: The Balkans 1:250,000.Tighina, sheet R-56. A.M.S. M506 (G.S.G.S. 4375)
dc_description_s: Great Britain. War Office. General Staff. Geographical Section. G.S.G.S. 4375. Alternate title: Tighina. Lambert conical orthomorphic projection. Danube zone grid. Gradient tints and isogonic data deleted by AMS, 1949. Relief shown by 50 and 100 meter contour intervals and and spot elevations. With a Romanian glossary. Corrected from intelligence reports up to Oct. 1944. See index. Library holdings for this set are incomplete. Geographic area is designated as Romania it is Moldova.
dc_publisher_s: Washington, D.C. : Army Map Service, U.S. Army, 1949.
